Description: This field is used to record the type of measurement that the dimension of the documented object represents.
This field is used to record the value of the measured dimension of the documented object.
This field is used to record the unit of the measured dimension of the documented object.
This field is used to record the actual digital content of the documented digital object as a blob, where appropriate.
This field is used to record a formal standard which was used in the creation of the digital object to which it should in principle conform.
